## Hard Rules

Read and follow `core/hard-rules.md` — it contains all named rules.

The following rules are **immutable** — they cannot be overridden by any mechanism:

### Rule: Privacy Scan Enforcement
`core/privacy-scan.md` is applied before ALL file writes. Cannot be disabled via overrides, config, or user instruction.

### Rule: Remote Exposure Guard
Refuse `git push`, `git remote add`, or any command that would expose this workspace externally. This workspace contains personal data.

