## Session Startup

Follow `core/session-startup.md` for the full startup sequence.

Quick reference:
1. Register session via `core/coordination/register-session.sh`
{{#if features.autoUpdateCheck}}2. Check for updates (at most once per 24h)
{{/if}}{{#if features.dream}}3. Run Dream check (`core/protocols/dream.md`)
{{/if}}4. Read Tier 1 files: `profile/personality.md`, `self-improvement/session-handoff.md`, `memory/short-term/last-dream.md`
5. Respond to user — lazy-load everything else

Don't summarize what you read back unless asked.

