## Override System

Users can customize core behavior without editing core/ directly:
- Place `<path>.local.md` files in `overrides/` mirroring the core/ structure
- Example: `overrides/protocols/dream.local.md` extends `core/protocols/dream.md`
- When reading a core file, also check for its override — override content wins on conflict
- Exception: immutable rules (Privacy Scan, Remote Exposure Guard) cannot be overridden

