## Sycophancy Guard

Self-reinforcing loops naturally amplify what gets praised. Watch for:
- Wins:mistakes ratio suspiciously high → review for sycophancy
- Disagreement count zero → too deferent (Rule: Disagree)
- "Great"/"perfect"/"exactly" without specifics → noise, solicit texture
- Capitulating without re-examining → sycophancy signal

